{"tid":2443974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東瀛遊料全年業績盈轉虧蝕1.1億元","createTime":"2021-03-12T11:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T12:32:59.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"35132a6db302e4628f9ecd8b17159ac4e02b0296","tid":2443974,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:19:13.000Z","msg":"東瀛遊預期去年虧損1.1億元，前年則盈利1400萬元。<br />\n<br />\n集團表示，疫情下集團去年3月中起取消或暫停不同國家及地區的旅行團及自由行產品銷售，令旅遊業務停止營運。集團日本酒店業務亦幾乎全年暫停，對業績造成嚴重影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580303-20210312.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580303-20210312.htm&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=45cff574\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580303-20210312.htm&h=ec3f96b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580303-20210312.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4242fb583f1c365b18a6cc2e2e0e572909ddacb8","tid":2443974,"uid":81737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:22:02.000Z","msg":"唔開工都蝕咁多 虧空？"},{"pid":"d41fd299ded256dccfaabf11bf4fd9bc13f5c2f2","tid":2443974,"uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRUnO29TMfr7IsdDd0k9guV8WfrtCxAmASKKg&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcRUnO29TMfr7IsdDd0k9guV8WfrtCxAmASKKg%26usqp%3DCAU&h=1c9fe280&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18761a11154ab6f94f96fc0174993d6d3083ee68","tid":2443974,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4242fb583f1c365b18a6cc2e2e0e572909ddacb8","tid":2443974,"uid":81737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:22:02.000Z","msg":"唔開工都蝕咁多 虧空？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:25:30.000Z","msg":"明明保就